data.name: Label16.Text
data.value: Combinator can combine two or three Wordlists. Every word of the second and third wordlist is appended to the first wordlist. Comparable to the combination attack (-a 1). You can find the output file in the folder "#_Wordlists".

data.name: Label23.Text
data.value: With "Len" you can extract password candidates with a certain length from Wordlists into a new Wordlist. For example, you could extract all passwords with a minimum length of 8 from the rockyou.txt.
